modules.description: Provides network protocol parsing and serialization functions, including TCP, UDP, and IP layers, with support for packet inspection and modification. Operates on byte sequences and custom-defined protocol data structures. Used to build lightweight, high-performance network services such as DNS proxies and HTTP load balancers within unikernel environments.

Provides network, block, and time interfaces for MirageOS, including operations for packet transmission, disk I/O, and time management. Works with Lwt-based asynchronous data types such as promises and event loops. Used to build unikernels with specific hardware or protocol dependencies.
